  "prompt": "What are some good dance club songs?",
  "response": "Here are some popular dance club songs that are often enjoyed for their upbeat tempos and energetic vibes:\n\n1. **\"Don't Start Now\" by Dua Lipa**\n2. **\"Blinding Lights\" by The Weeknd**\n3. **\"Levitating\" by Dua Lipa ft. DaBaby**\n4. **\"Uptown Funk\" by Mark Ronson ft. Bruno Mars**\n5. **\"Taki Taki\" by DJ Snake ft. Selena Gomez, Ozuna & Cardi B**\n6. **\"Bad Guy\" by Billie Eilish**\n7. **\"ROCKSTAR\" by DaBaby ft. Roddy Ricch**\n8. **\"Shape of You\" by Ed Sheeran**\n9. **\"Rain On Me\" by Lady Gaga & Ariana Grande**\n10. **\"One Kiss\" by Calvin Harris & Dua Lipa**\n11. **\"Dance Monkey\" by Tones and I**\n12. **\"Savage Love\" by Jawsh 685 & Jason Derulo**\n13. **\"Despacito\" (Remix) by Luis Fonsi & Daddy Yankee ft. Justin Bieber**\n14. **\"Dynamite\" by BTS**\n15. **\"Closer\" by The Chainsmokers ft. Halsey**\n\nThese tracks are known for their infectious beats and are commonly played in dance clubs around the world. If you're hosting a party or looking to create a dance playlist, these songs are great additions.",
